'''洛聖都'''（{{lang-en|'''Los Santos'''}}，縮寫為'''LS'''）<ref name="ls&blaine_zhtw">{{Cite web |url=http://www.rockstargames.com/V/zh_tw/info/lossantosandblainecounty |title=洛聖都 和 布萊恩郡 |accessdate=2013-11-30 |author=Rockstar Games |language= zh-tw }}</ref>是[[Rockstar_North|Rockstar North]]開發、[[Rockstar_Games|Rockstar Games]]發行的系列遊戲《[[俠盜獵車手系列|俠盜獵車手]]》裡面的一座虛構城市。它以美國[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]]的城市[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]為創作依據。與洛杉磯相似的，洛聖都包括了若干不同的地區，市區也擁有著與洛杉磯相當的人口數量以及圍繞在周邊的[[都會區|都會區]]。

雖然[[聖安地列斯_(俠盜獵車手)|聖安地列斯州]]早已在[[俠盜獵車手_(遊戲)|俠盜獵車手第一代]]登場，洛聖都僅在其中兩部作品中出現，分別為2004年發行的《[[俠盜獵車手：聖安地列斯|俠盜獵車手：聖安地列斯]]》和2013年的《[[俠盜獵車手V|俠盜獵車手V]]》。在《聖安地列斯》一作中，洛聖都被聖輝洛（San Fierro）和拉斯雲組華（Las Venturas）兩座城市所包圍，城市與城市之間被郊區所分隔；不過在《俠盜獵車手V》中，洛聖都以單一城市出現，在其北方還坐落著布雷恩郡<ref name="ls&blaine_zhtw"/>（Blaine County）。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://metro.co.uk/2011/11/03/los-santos-is-only-city-in-grand-theft-auto-v-206685/ |title=Los Santos is only city in Grand Theft Auto V |author=GameCentral |publisher=''[[Metro_(British_newspaper)|Metro]] |date=2011-11-03 |accessdate=2013-08-26 |archive-date=2013-09-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130901084910/http://metro.co.uk/2011/11/03/los-santos-is-only-city-in-grand-theft-auto-v-206685/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>在兩部遊戲中，洛聖都都有著各式各樣的商業機構供玩家購買以產生收入。 <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/gaming/viva-los-santos--a-city-of-guns-cars-and-yoga-grand-theft-auto-v-also-offers-some-middleclass-pursuits-amid-the-mayhem-8831838.html |title=Viva Los Santos – a city of guns, cars... and yoga: Grand Theft Auto V also offers some middle-class pursuits amid the mayhem |last=Sherwin |first=Adam |publisher=''[[The_Independent|The Independent]]'' |date=2013-09-22 |accessdate=2013-10-02 |archive-date=2015-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925043438/http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/gaming/viva-los-santos--a-city-of-guns-cars-and-yoga-grand-theft-auto-v-also-offers-some-middleclass-pursuits-amid-the-mayhem-8831838.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

俠盜獵車手V的地圖大小（即洛聖都及其周邊的郊區）比《[[俠盜獵車手IV|俠盜獵車手IV]]》中的自由城和《[[荒野大镖客：救赎|荒野大镖客：救赎]]》的地圖加起來還要大。<ref name="GTA V Biggest World">{{cite web |url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/377702/gta-v-world-is-bigger-than-red-dead-redemption-san-andreas-and-gta-4-combined/ |title=GTA V world 'is bigger than Red Dead Redemption, San Andreas and GTA 4 combined' |last=Hussain |first=Tamoor |work=[[Computer_and_Video_Games|Computer and Video Games]] |date=2012-11-08 |accessdate=2012-11-10 |archive-date=2012-11-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121110032812/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/377702/gta-v-world-is-bigger-than-red-dead-redemption-san-andreas-and-gta-4-combined/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2013/09/16/gta-5-size-map-comparison_n_3934418.html?utm_hp_ref=mostpopular |title=GTA 5: How Big Is Los Santos Compared To Real Cities? (PICTURE) |author=Huffington Post UK |publisher=''[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]]'' |date=2013-09-16 |accessdate=2013-10-02 |archive-date=2017-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170917080502/http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2013/09/16/gta-5-size-map-comparison_n_3934418.html?utm_hp_ref=mostpopular |dead-url=no }}</ref>這也是目前Rockstar Games製作的遊戲中規模最大的開放世界<ref name="ls&blaine_zhtw"/>。

== 開發 ==
[[Image:LosAngeles06.jpg|thumb]]景觀]]

在《聖安地列斯》和《俠盜獵車手V》中，洛聖都均以洛杉磯作為其創作樣本。<ref name="GTA V Back To San Andreas">{{cite web |publisher=Wired |first=Jason |last=Schreier |url=http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2011/11/grand-theft-auto-5-trailer/ |title=Grand Theft Auto V Rolls Back to San Andreas |date=2011-11-02 |accessdate=2012-03-15 |archive-date=2011-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111102202328/http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2011/11/grand-theft-auto-5-trailer/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.slate.com/blogs/moneybox/2013/09/23/grand_theft_economics_why_no_traffic_jams_in_los_santos.html |title=Grand Theft Economics: Why no traffic jams in Los Santos. |last=Yglesias |first=Matthew |publisher=''[[Slate_(magazine)|Slate]]'' |date=2013-09-23 |accessdate=2013-10-02 |archive-date=2018-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180505064157/http://www.slate.com/blogs/moneybox/2013/09/23/grand_theft_economics_why_no_traffic_jams_in_los_santos.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 這座虛構城市濃縮了洛杉磯代表事物，包括了與洛杉磯相似的地標建築和區域，但在遊戲中以不同的名稱設置在不同的地點。其中一個例子就是遊戲中的「[[好萊塢|好萊塢]]」被稱為「好麥塢」。<ref name="newyorker"/>

為了《俠盜獵車手V》的開發，開發團隊對洛杉磯進行了徹底的研究。他們組織了實地考察行程，並與當地導遊和建築歷史學家一同進行考察；行程中，他們拍攝了約250,000張照片和幾個小時的錄影片段。<ref name="Building the World Of GTA V">{{cite web |publisher=[[BuzzFeed|BuzzFeed]] |first=Joseph |last=Bernstein |url=http://www.buzzfeed.com/josephbernstein/way-beyond-anything-weve-done-before-building-the-world-of-g |title="Way Beyond Anything We’ve Done Before": Building The World Of "Grand Theft Auto V" |date=2013-08-13 |accessdate=2013-09-03 |archive-date=2013-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130815073123/http://www.buzzfeed.com/josephbernstein/way-beyond-anything-weve-done-before-building-the-world-of-g |dead-url=no }}</ref>

