洛聖都展示了許多經過藝術加工的洛杉磯地區、地標建築和居民區，其中包括[[康普顿_(加利福尼亚州)|康普頓]]、[[英格爾伍德_(加利福尼亞州)|英格蘭伍德]]、東洛杉磯（東洛聖都，East Los Santos）、[[麥克阿瑟公園|麥克阿瑟公園]]（格林公園，Glen Park）、洛杉磯市中心（洛聖都市中心，Downtown Los Santos）、[[比佛利山_(加利福尼亞州)|比佛利山]]（羅克福特山，Rockford Hills）、[[穆赫蘭大道|穆赫蘭大道]]（穆赫蘭，Mulholland）、[[圣莫尼卡|圣莫尼卡]]（聖瑪麗亞海灘，Santa Maria Beach）、[[马利布_(加利福尼亚州)|馬利布]]（丘瑪墟，Chumash）、[[威尼斯_(洛杉磯)|威尼斯海灘]]（威斯普奇海灘，Vespucci Beach）和好萊塢（好麥塢，Vinewood）及山上的[[好萊塢標誌|好萊塢標誌]]（好麥塢招牌，Vinewood Sign）。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.g-unleashed.com/index.php?jump=313 |title=Los Santos Properties GTA: San Andreas |author=Chaos Energy |publisher=G-Unleashed |accessdate=2013-09-13 |archive-date=2019-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190828092510/http://www.g-unleashed.com/index.php?jump=313 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 評價 ===
在《[[俠盜獵車手V|俠盜獵車手V]]》發布之後，洛聖都獲得了評論家的高度評價。[[PlayStation官方雜誌|PlayStation官方雜誌]]的Joel Gregory和[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]]的Hollander Cooper讚揚地圖的大小與細節；他們通過與前作作出對比，認為洛聖都要比《[[俠盜獵車手IV|俠盜獵車手IV]]》的[[自由城_(俠盜獵車手)|自由城]]「更吸引人」。<ref name="OPM UK Review">{{cite web |url=http://www.officialplaystationmagazine.co.uk/review/gta-5-ps3-review-grand-theft-auto-v-score-from-official-playstation-magazine/ |title=GTA 5 PS3 review – Three men and a little LA deed sign the generation off in style |last=Gregory |first=Joel |date=2013-09-16 |publisher=[[PlayStation_Official_Magazine|PlayStation Official Magazine]] |accessdate=2013-09-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131219050729/http://www.officialplaystationmagazine.co.uk/review/gta-5-ps3-review-grand-theft-auto-v-score-from-official-playstation-magazine/ |archivedate=2013-12-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="GRadar">{{cite web |last=Cooper |first=Hollander |url=http://www.gamesradar.com/gta-5-review/ |title=GTA 5 review |publisher=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]] |date= |accessdate=2013-09-17 |archive-date=2013-10-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131012110336/http://www.gamesradar.com/gta-5-review/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[IGN|IGN]]的Keza MacDonald也表達了同樣的觀點，同時她稱讚了遊戲世界的高開放度，並認為探索這座城市是一件很令人享受的事。<ref name="IGN Review">{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/09/16/grand-theft-auto-v-review |title=Grand Theft Auto V Review |last=MacDonald |first=Keza |date=2013-09-16 |publisher=IGN |accessdate=2013-09-16 |archive-date=2013-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130916190840/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/09/16/grand-theft-auto-v-review |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[Polygon|Polygon]]的Chris Plante感嘆道遊戲世界是多麼的令人難以置信。<ref name="Polygon Review">{{cite web |url=http://www.polygon.com/2013/9/16/4720458/gta-5-review-grand-theft-auto |title=Grand Theft Auto 5 review: golden years |last=Plante |first=Chris |publisher=[[Polygon|Polygon]] |date=2013-09-16 |accessdate=2013-09-17 |archive-date=2013-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130918051659/http://www.polygon.com/2013/9/16/4720458/gta-5-review-grand-theft-auto |dead-url=no }}</ref>

許多評論家讚揚了[[開放世界|開放世界]]的規模，並對遊戲所呈現的洛杉磯城市景象給予讚賞。[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]的Tom Bramwell和[[Destructoid|Destructoid]]的Jim Sterling讚揚遊戲將洛杉磯的地理整合到了一個多種多樣且巧妙設計的城市空間中。<ref name="Eurogamer Review">{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-09-16-grand-theft-auto-5-review |title=Grand Theft Auto 5 review |last=Bramwell |first=Tom |publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |date=2013-09-16 |accessdate=2013-09-17 |archive-date=2013-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130918045510/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-09-16-grand-theft-auto-5-review |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Destructoid Review">{{cite web |url=http://www.destructoid.com/review-grand-theft-auto-v-261879.phtml |title=Review: Grand Theft Auto V |last=Sterling |first=Jim |date=2013-09-16 |publisher=[[Destructoid|Destructoid]] |accessdate=2013-09-16 |archive-date=2013-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131014073952/http://www.destructoid.com/review-grand-theft-auto-v-261879.phtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[Giant_Bomb|Giant Bomb]]的Jeff Gertsmann稱這座城市「很好地勾起人們對[[洛杉矶|洛杉磯]]的回憶」。<ref name="Giant Bomb Review">{{cite web |url=http://www.giantbomb.com/reviews/grand-theft-auto-v-review/1900-598/ |title=Grand Theft Auto V Review |last=Gertsmann |first=Jeff |date=2013-09-16 |publisher=[[Giant_Bomb|Giant Bomb]] |accessdate=2013-09-16 |archive-date=2013-09-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130917171256/http://www.giantbomb.com/reviews/grand-theft-auto-v-review/1900-598/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> [[GameTrailers|GameTrailers]]的Brandon Jones稱這座城市是一座[[洛杉矶|洛杉磯]][[地標|地標]]建築的有趣組合。<ref name="gametrailers">{{cite web|url=http://www.gametrailers.com/reviews/3d7x5s/grand-theft-auto-v-review|accessdate=2013-09-17|title=Grand Theft Auto V Review|publisher=[[GameTrailers|GameTrailers]]|date=September 2013|archive-date=2013-09-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130920002718/http://www.gametrailers.com/reviews/3d7x5s/grand-theft-auto-v-review|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

